title: Taylor (Helena MJ)
body: An Englishwoman who lived in Madeira for many years and died in England in October 1907, at the age of about 65. E. :Madeira-: its scenery, and how to see it (London, 1882). In this work, there is a list of ferns and another of Madeiran marine algae.

Madeira: Island where Helena MJ Taylor lived

1882: Publication of :Madeira-: its scenery, and how to see it
